War and Peace 



BY LEO TOLSTOY 



Translated b\ LOUISE and AYLMER MAUDE 




WILLIAM BENTON, Publisher 



ENCYCLOPEDIA BR1TANNICA, INC. 



CHICAGO - LONDON - TORONTO 



