Prince Vasfli Kurdgin, an elderly nobleman 

Prince Hippolyte Kurdgin, his weak-minded elder son 

Prince Anatole Kurdgin, his profligate younger son 

Princess Hdlene Kunigina, his daughter, "the beautiful Helene" 

